# Safe Editing For Jekyll Repo

- Never edit `_site/**` directly.
- Never edit `node_modules/**`.
- Prefer changing only source markdown/config files.
- For vacancy tooling: edit **`job/channel-checkpoints.json`** for crawl/match state; keep **`job/job-channels.md`** as URL list only unless adding/removing sources.
